text: William Milroy (born 11 September 1980) is a professional badminton player. A resident of Edmonton, he has been a Men's Doubles Winner in the Canadian National Badminton Championships in each year since 2004.Badminton Canada ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Edmonton Category:Badminton players at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Canadian male badminton players Category:Pan American Games competitors for Canada Category:Pan American Games medalists in badminton Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Canada Category:Badminton players at the 2006 Commonwealth Games Category:Badminton players at the 2002 Commonwealth Games
